Interface IIconLibrary

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IconLibrary, IconLibrary, IconLibrary, IconLibrary, IconLibrary, IconLibrary, IconLibrary, IconLibrary, IconLibraryBase

    public interface IIconLibrary
    Interface for plug-in icon libraries.

    • Method Summary

      Returns the relative path for the requested icon.

    • Method Detail

      • getId

        String getId()
        Returns the unique identifier for the library.
        Returns:
        The unique identifier.

      • getIconPath

        String getIconPath(String iconName,
                   String dimensions)
        Returns the relative path for the requested icon.
        Parameters:
        iconName - The icon file name.
        dimensions - The desired dimensions (for example, 16x16). May be null for default dimensions.
        Returns:
        The relative path referencing the requested icon.

      • getMatching

        List<String> getMatching(String iconName,
                         String dimensions)
        Returns a list of relative paths for icons that match the criteria. Criteria may include wildcard characters. For example, getMatching("weather*", "*x16")
        Parameters:
        iconName - Name of icon to match.
        dimensions - Desired dimensions to match. May be null for default dimensions.
        Returns:
        List of matching paths.

      • supportedDimensions

        String[] supportedDimensions()
        Returns an array of dimensions supported by this library.
        Returns:
        Array of supported dimensions.
